title: Microsoft Office Professional Plus 2019 Preview Build 10301 LPs
description:
Microsoft Office Professional Plus 2019 Preview 1807 (Build 16.0.10301.20006)

Optional: Microsoft Project Professional 2019 Preview 1807 (Build 16.0.10301.20006) and Microsoft Visio Professional 2019 Preview 1807 (Build 16.0.10301.20006)

Languages: Arabic (Saudi Arabia), Czech (Czech Republic), Chinese (PRC), Danish (Denmark), German (Germany), Greek (Greece), English (United States), Spanish (Spain), French (France), Hebrew (Israel), Hindi (India), Hungarian (Hungary), Italian (Italy), Japanese (Japan), Korean (Korea), Norwegian, Bokmål (Norway), Dutch (Netherlands), Polish (Poland), Portuguese (Brazil), Romanian (Romania), Russian (Russia), Swedish (Sweden), Turkish (Turkey), Ukrainian (Ukraine) and Vietnamese (Viet Nam)

Channel: Current Insider Preview Fast

Credits: Click-to-Run (C2R) installation provided by Ratiborus

To prepare:

1. Uninstall Microsoft Office 2016 (or any MSO version installed) Use Click2UnistallOfficeApps.diagcab if needed.
2. Windows 10 Installed (Windows 8.1/8/7/Vista are not supported)
	
How to Install:
1. On the Main tab of the installer, select "Microsoft Office 2019"
2. Select x86 or x64
3. Confirm office version and single products
4. Click install office
5. Click ok (keep current channel)
	   
How to Update: In the application menu, go to "File>Account>Office Updates"

Due to resource limitations, please help me seed these distributions
